I watched a video of a supposed exorcism about a year ago. The girl that claimed to be possessed was attempting to throw up the sign of the devil. I say attempting because I've been an underground metalhead for over 20 years so I know how to correctly throw up the horns. 

   You have to tuck in your thumb. If your thumb is out that's sign language for I love you. It's a common misconception that the sign for I Iove you and the sign of the devil are the same. This girl that was claiming to be possessed was throwing up the sign for I love you as if it was the sign of the devil. 

   I guess whatever infernal demon that was supposedly possessing her didn't have enough demonic knowledge to know how to throw up the horns correctly. So needless to say I don't think you really have a whole lot to worry about in terms of demonic possession. Even the Catholic Church regards over 95% or more of cases of claimed demonic possession to actually be cases of mental illness.
